This is a demo code for the Grove Sound Recorder Twig to be able to be controlled programmatically.
The serial commands are:
#rb = begin recording track #
#rs/rs = stop all recording
#p = play track # 
rm = record mode
pm = play mode

Example usage:
To record at #4 slot
: rm
: 4rb
<then record the sound>
: 4rs

To play #4 slot:
: pm
: 4p
